data.description: Welcome home to this prime location beautiful 2 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom townhome style condo. This property boasts two family rooms, one on the lower level and the second on the upper level with a balcony attached. The ensuite is spacious with two walk-in closets. The property is centrally located  to multiple military installations to include; Joint Bases Andrews and Boiling, the Pentagon, Washington, DC, the beltway, and many additional locations in the DMV area.
